analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: Defensive rotation intensifies amid regime volatility. The GMS score of 52 dictates a transition into an equilibrium of caution as the VIX breach of the 20-threshold signals imminent regime degradation. While credit spread compression remains persistent, the divergence between industrial commodities and precious metals underscores a flight to quality. Stagnant net liquidity coupled with a sharp deceleration in crypto sentiment necessitates a pivot from aggressive beta-exposure toward high-conviction defensive tranches to mitigate liquidity convexity. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

reports.EN: Defensive rotation intensifies amid regime volatility. The GMS score of 52 dictates a transition into an equilibrium of caution as the VIX breach of the 20-threshold signals imminent regime degradation. While credit spread compression remains persistent, the divergence between industrial commodities and precious metals underscores a flight to quality. Stagnant net liquidity coupled with a sharp deceleration in crypto sentiment necessitates a pivot from aggressive beta-exposure toward high-conviction defensive tranches to mitigate liquidity convexity.
